workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
How does Chris get those thunderous arms? You're about to find out. This workout is loaded with new moves to get your back and biceps flying â€“ make the tutorial your first stop.


You'll be doing a lot of reps, so keep your form tight and make every single lift count.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: Get your upper body primed to hit the racks.

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: This is a big lift and you'll be doing 5 sets, so pace yourself and make sure your form is on point.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: If you speed through your first set, add weight to up the challenge.

groups.title: Round 3
groups.summary: Engage your core and get pulling to work your lats, traps, biceps and more.

groups.title: Round 4
groups.summary: There's a new grip in town, so be sure to run through the tutorial for these single-arm rows.

groups.title: Round 5
groups.summary: Focus on tempo to maximize time under tension.
